additional-services-txt: Interested in borrowing or lending your car? Taking part in and organising cookery classes? Or helping someone with their day-to-day problems? Then pay your annual subscription and access all our services between private individuals!

errorOtherProductNameCategory: Information is missing on at least one of the new products you wish to add to our catalog. Please make sure that you have filled in the name and category of all the orange-bordered products in your donation list.

home_txt_1: No More Waste collects food donations from retailers and individuals. Anyone in need can apply for a portion of these donations. As an association, we rely on volunteers to help with the collection and dispatch of foodstuffs on our rounds.
home_txt_car: Access our car exchange service by paying a small fee.
home_txt_cooking: Take part in cooking classes and advice sessions to avoid food waste.
home_txt_donation: Contribute to our cause by making a donation to support our efforts.
home_txt_project: Get help from the community for small DIY jobs.
home_txt_volunteer: Join our team of volunteers and help us collect and distribute food.
join-us-txt: Do you want to be able to give away what you don't need? Give your time to help those in need? Or do you want someone to help you when you need it?

orderSuccessMessage: Your request has been successfully registered. We will add it to one of our distribution tours as soon as possible.
